===Noun===
{{en-noun|-|head=[[modern|Modern]] [[Greek]]}}

# The [[Greek]] language is that which has been spoken by the Greek people since the [[w:Fall of Constantinople|fall of Constantinople]] in 1453. It was written using [[polytonic]] script until 1982, when this was officially dropped in favour of [[monotonic]].

